{
  "id": "adv_event_2208_01_02",
  "title": "夏になんか\n負けない",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――半月後",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――2 weeks after",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0,
      "endTime": 1.3,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_zawa-01.m4a",
          "delay": 1433.3333333
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shibuya-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "shibuya-00-noon",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2208_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2208_01_02-ai001.m4a",
      "text": "今日は猛暑日か……どうりで、暑いはずだよ\nあっ、こころ！　こっち！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It's scorching hot today…it's so hot.\nAh‚ Kokoro! Over here!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 2.2333333333,
      "endTime": 9.3333335121,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-out-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 7286.6668383
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shibuya-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "shibuya-00-noon",
      "startTime": 7
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shibuya-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "shibuya-00-noon",
      "startTime": 9.5200001716
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2208_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2208_01_02-kkr001.m4a",
      "text": "今日も暑いね～、愛\nこころのせっかくの美肌が焼けちゃうよ……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It's so hot again‚ Ai.\nKokoro's beautiful skin will get tanned…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 11.1533335049,
      "endTime": 18.0131293855,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shibuya-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "shibuya-00-noon",
      "startTime": 18.213129425
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2208_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2208_01_02-ai002.m4a",
      "text": "自分で言わない。後、ぐでっとしないの\n先輩達は今も頑張って新曲の企画を練ってるんだから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Don't say that to yourself. Also‚ don't slouch.\nSenpais are still working hard on planning the new song.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 18.213129425,
      "endTime": 26.6824943179,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shibuya-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "shibuya-00-noon",
      "startTime": 26.8558275859
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2208_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2208_01_02-ai003.m4a",
      "text": "後輩の私達がダラけてる訳にはいかないでしょ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "We can't slack off as juniors‚ right?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 26.8558275859,
      "endTime": 30.244081560799998,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shibuya-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "shibuya-00-noon",
      "startTime": 30.4307483037
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2208_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2208_01_02-kkr002.m4a",
      "text": "分かってるよ～。だから、こうしてアイスを持って\n陣中見舞いに行くんじゃない……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I know that. That's why I brought ice cream.\nWe're here to give our support…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 30.4307483037,
      "endTime": 37.6594105127,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shibuya-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "shibuya-00-noon",
      "startTime": 37.8594104449
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2208_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2208_01_02-ai004.m4a",
      "text": "それにしても、莉央さんも葵さんも凄いよね\nオフも自主練して企画を立てて、ストイックっていうか",
      "translations": {
        "en": "By the way‚ Rio-san and Aoi-san are amazing.\nThey even practice on their days off and plan everything themselves. It's so dedicated.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 37.8594104449,
      "endTime": 47.8317002085,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shibuya-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "shibuya-00-noon",
      "startTime": 48.0317001025
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2208_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2208_01_02-kkr003.m4a",
      "text": "ストイック過ぎ！　こころは夏休みくらい\n四人で遊びに行きたかったのに～",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Too dedicated! I wanted to go out with the four of us during summer vacation.\nBut here I am…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 48.0317001025,
      "endTime": 54.200044764699996,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shibuya-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "shibuya-00-noon",
      "startTime": 54.4000446637
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2208_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2208_01_02-ai005.m4a",
      "text": "え？　こころも？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Eh? You too‚ Kokoro?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 54.4000446637,
      "endTime": 56.634625109,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2208_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2208_01_02-kkr004.m4a",
      "text": "当然だよ～。海水浴やキャンプに花火……\n夏を四人で満喫したかったのに～",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Of course! I wanted the four of us to enjoy summer together—\ngoing to the beach‚ camping‚ fireworks…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 56.9666666667,
      "endTime": 64.6506201713,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shibuya-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "shibuya-00-noon",
      "startTime": 60.9333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shibuya-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "shibuya-00-noon",
      "startTime": 65.0333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2208_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2208_01_02-kkr005.m4a",
      "text": "四人で曲作りの名目で遊びに行くつもりが\nまさか莉央さんと葵さんが引きこもっちゃうなんて",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I planned to use songwriting as an excuse to hang out.\nNever expected Rio-san and Aoi-san to turn into homebodies.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 65.0333333333,
      "endTime": 72.8304426944,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shibuya-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "shibuya-00-noon",
      "startTime": 73
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2208_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2208_01_02-ai006.m4a",
      "text": "こころがそういう方向に持って行ったんだからね\n……実は私も、四人で遊びたかったんだけど",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Well‚ you were the one who brought it up in that direction…\n…Actually‚ I also wanted to hang out with the four of us.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 73,
      "endTime": 80.73489895040001,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shibuya-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "shibuya-00-noon",
      "startTime": 76.7
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shibuya-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "shibuya-00-noon",
      "startTime": 80.9333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2208_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2208_01_02-ai007.m4a",
      "text": "でも今更、外に遊びに行こうなんて絶対言えないよ\nそんな空気じゃないもん！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But now‚ I can't possibly say‚ \"Let's go out together!\"\nIt's just not the right atmosphere!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 80.9333333333,
      "endTime": 87.21608932240001,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shibuya-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "shibuya-00-noon",
      "startTime": 87.4
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2208_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2208_01_02-kkr006.m4a",
      "text": "だよね～。二人とも融通が利かないのが玉にキズだよ\nこころを見習ってほしいよ～",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yeah‚ both of them not budging is a bummer.\nThey should learn from Kokoro.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 87.4,
      "endTime": 95.25054358930001,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2208_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2208_01_02-kkr007.m4a",
      "text": "なんとかして、一緒に遊びに行けないかな～\nあ、寝込みを襲って拉致しちゃう？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I wish we could find a way to go out together.\nOh‚ how about we ambush them in their sleep and kidnap them?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 95.4333333333,
      "endTime": 101.79243643960001,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shibuya-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "shibuya-00-noon",
      "startTime": 101.9666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2208_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2208_01_02-ai008.m4a",
      "text": "怖いよ！　こころ、何言ってるの！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Scary! Kokoro‚ what are you saying!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 101.9666666667,
      "endTime": 104.84260775249999,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shibuya-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "shibuya-00-noon",
      "startTime": 105.0333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2208_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2208_01_02-kkr008.m4a",
      "text": "半分冗談だよ～～\n半分は本気だけど",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Half-joking‚ you know~\nBut half-serious.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 105.0333333333,
      "endTime": 109.06748302380001,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shibuya-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "shibuya-00-noon",
      "startTime": 109.2333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2208_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2208_01_02-ai009.m4a",
      "text": "半分でもダメだよ……もう",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Half is still a no… Enough!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 109.2333333333,
      "endTime": 113.1047392209,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-living-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 5366.666666699999
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2208_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2208_01_02-kkr009.m4a",
      "text": "失礼しまーす。先輩方\n企画の進み具合はどうですか～～？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Excuse me‚ senpais.\nHow's the progress of the plan?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 116.1333333333,
      "endTime": 121.4658059486,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2208_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2208_01_02-kkr010.m4a",
      "text": "アイス買って来ましたので一休み――って\n部屋の中あっつ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I brought ice cream for a break—wait.\nIt's sweltering in here!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 121.6666666667,
      "endTime": 127.31551443880001,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2208_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2208_01_02-rio001.m4a",
      "text": "……な、夏ってなんなのよ…………",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…What's with this summer…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 127.4666666667,
      "endTime": 131.0050566356,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2208_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2208_01_02-aoi001.m4a",
      "text": "夏は……夏なんだ、多分、きっと……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It's summer… it's just summer‚ probably‚ I guess…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 131.2333333333,
      "endTime": 137.5640817006,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2208_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2208_01_02-ai010.m4a",
      "text": "きゃーっ！　せ、先輩方が倒れて……！？\nまさか、し、し、死んで……！？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Kyaa! S-Senpais collapsed…!?\nDon't tell me they're d-d-dead…!?",
        "id": ""
      },
